      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:470:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/450/570",
      "text": [
        "۴۵۰. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَا مَزَحَ امْرُؤٌ مَزْحَةً إِلَّا مَجَّ مِنْ عَقْلِهِ مَجَّةً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "450. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Whenever a man cuts a joke he separates away a bit from his wit."
        ]
      }
